      "content": "That makes sense. I guess it depends on how much a company is expected to prepare for infrastructure instability. If the surge was caused by a sequence of minor, cascading failures rather than one big event, how does that affect the \"unforeseeable\" argument? Does the cumulative nature of the disruption change the legal interpretation?",
